<h1>About the Materials Management System</h1>

<%=@about_me%>

<p>The Materials Management System is designed to help educators, administrators, and organizations keep track of their valuable resources. Whether you're managing classroom supplies, electronics, or tools, this app ensures everything stays organized.</p>

<h2>Why Use This System?</h2>
<ul>
  <li>✅ Reduce material loss by tracking who checked out what and when.</li>
  <li>✅ Improve efficiency by quickly locating materials.</li>
  <li>✅ Simplify check-in/check-out with automated logging.</li>
  <li>✅ Provide accountability with instructor assignments.</li>
</ul>

<h2>How It Works:</h2>
<ol>
  <li>📝 Add materials to the inventory.</li>
  <li>🏷 Assign a location and responsible instructor.</li>
  <li>🔄 Check materials in and out as needed.</li>
  <li>📊 Keep a record of usage history for better management.</li>
</ol>

<p>My goal is to make inventory management simple, fast, and reliable. Start using the system today and take control of your materials!</p>

